title: Irish shut down Georgia to reach CFP semifinals
description: Carried by its defense and special teams, Notre Dame made enough big plays to topple No. 2 Georgia 23-10 in the Sugar Bowl and reach the semifinals of the College Football Playoff.

title: LeBron, Curry 3rd at positions in All-Star voting
description: Milwaukee's Giannis Antetokounmpo is the early leader in fan balloting for the NBA All-Star Game, and LeBron James of the Los Angeles Lakers seems well on his way toward extending his record and getting picked for a 21st time.
author: Tim Bontemps

title: Littler thrashes Bunting to set up Van Gerwen final
description: Teenager Luke Littler thrashes Stephen Bunting 6-1 with a ruthless display to set up a PDC World Championship final against Michael van Gerwen on Friday.

title: Rangers condemn incident in which Engels hit by coin
description: Rangers condemn "in the strongest possible terms" an incident in which Celtic's Arne Engels was struck by a coin during Thursday's Old Firm game.

title: Notre Dame wins Sugar Bowl to reach CFP semifinals
description: The Fighting Irish rolled past Georgia to end their 31-year major bowl losing skid, setting up a showdown vs. Penn State in next week's Orange Bowl.
author: Yahoo Sports

title: QB Room: All the pressing offseason questions, starting with the Raiders, Giants, Shedeur Sanders and Cam Ward
description: The two teams with the clearest need at QB are no longer in position to just sit and draft one. Plus, the Vikings' plans, Brock Purdy's extension situation, Aaron Rodgers' future and more.
author: Yahoo Sports

title: Littler sets up World Championship final showdown with MVG
description: Luke Littler demolished Stephen Bunting 6-1 to set up a World Darts Championship final against Michael van Gerwen at Alexandra Palace on Friday, live on Sky.

title: Joshua targeting Fury in 2025 as he vows to box on
description: Anthony Joshua is pursuing a fight with Tyson Fury in 2025 as he vows to carry on boxing after his crushing defeat to Daniel Dubois in September.
